snippet.title: Evercade Intellivision Collection 1 Trailer
snippet.description:
More Information: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/intellivision-collection-1

The Intellivision Collection 1 cartridge brings 12 classic Intellivision games to the Evercade! Including Astrosmash, Night Stalker, Frog Bog and more!

Games List:
- Astrosmash
- Buzz Bombers
- Frog Bog
- Night Stalker
- Pinball
- Princess Quest
- Shark Shark
- Slap Shot: Super Pro Hockey
- Snafu
- Thin Ice
- Thunder Castle
- Word Rockets
